<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="8">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$du-gu-bo-jue" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/du-gu-bo-jue" class="zg-link" title="独孤伯爵">独孤伯爵</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$kan-kan-bu-dong" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/kan-kan-bu-dong" class="zg-link" title="看看不懂">看看不懂</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-zhi-jun-72-91" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-zhi-jun-72-91" class="zg-link" title="王志军">王志军</a></span>
